  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/2d4d0e4d349805c65d91c44118ba3697.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In <strong>OneShot Challenge</strong>, you play as a meatball fighting to save your family in the world of food. Inside an ancient temple dominated by unpredictable enemies, deadly traps, and brutal bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You fire a single bullet</strong> and must survive until every enemy is <strong>ELIMINATED</strong>. Redirect the bullet with your frying pan, dodge the chaos around you, and master every movement. <strong>One mistake means starting over from scratch.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/4ba0abafc7816f7fdfdbe4304a0f8c07.poster.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/4ba0abafc7816f7fdfdbe4304a0f8c07.webm?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/4ba0abafc7816f7fdfdbe4304a0f8c07.mp4?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/25f0d2cb8a601f915f9ae786c6378510.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire your single bullet and use your frying pan to redirect it with precision;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge to survive the chaos around you;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate special frying pan abilities to control the battlefield;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every room demands positioning, awareness, and nerves of steel.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One mistake can cost everything.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/49908b561e8320f549cd5ce54cf20fa5.poster.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/49908b561e8320f549cd5ce54cf20fa5.webm?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/49908b561e8320f549cd5ce54cf20fa5.mp4?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/a12b2d568c3d39f6999fafe702b8f023.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 40 unique enemies with varied attack patterns;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully procedural system: rooms, enemies, and items change every run;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items and combinations that completely transform your playstyle;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Pomário, the merchant, to strengthen your journey.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every run is different.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Every build tells a story.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/57f5f5ba1a0f1f9b46af3cf33bff665a.poster.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/57f5f5ba1a0f1f9b46af3cf33bff665a.webm?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/57f5f5ba1a0f1f9b46af3cf33bff665a.mp4?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/581dea2999366ec7fdba36b3eb96a11f.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only one life per run;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brutal bosses that demand full mastery of the mechanics;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progression based on skill and adaptation;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/1b47e41590b2f394bd2e6e5ccd40040d.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span> </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/2d4d0e4d349805c65d91c44118ba3697.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">In <strong>OneShot Challenge</strong>, you play as a meatball fighting to save your family in the world of food. Inside an ancient temple dominated by unpredictable enemies, deadly traps, and brutal bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You fire a single bullet</strong> and must survive until every enemy is <strong>ELIMINATED</strong>. Redirect the bullet with your frying pan, dodge the chaos around you, and master every movement. <strong>One mistake means starting over from scratch.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/4ba0abafc7816f7fdfdbe4304a0f8c07.poster.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/4ba0abafc7816f7fdfdbe4304a0f8c07.webm?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/4ba0abafc7816f7fdfdbe4304a0f8c07.mp4?t=1774021350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4112690/extras/25f0d2cb8a601f915f9ae786c6378510.avif?t=1774021350\" width=1024 height=128 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire your single bullet and use your frying pan to redirect it with precision;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge to survive the chaos around you;</